 Air Force]]<ref name=\"World Air Forces 2019\"/>\n;{{Flag|Ethiopia}}\n* [[Ethiopian Air Force]]<ref name=\"World Air Forces 2019\"/>\n;{{Flag|Georgia}}\n* [[Georgian Air Force]]<ref name=\"World Air Forces 2019\"/>\n[[File:MI-35P FAP Peru.jpg|thumb|Peruvian Air Force Mi-25D]]\n;{{Flag|Guinea}}\n* [[Military of Guinea#Air Force|Guinean Air Force]]<ref name=\"World Air Forces 2019\"/>\n;{{HUN}}\n* [[Hungarian Air Force]]<ref name=\"World Air Forces 2019\"/>\n;{{Flag|India}}\n* [[Indian Air Force]]<ref name=\"World Air Forces 2019\"/>\n;{{IDN}}\n* [[Indonesian Army]]<ref name=\"World Air Forces 2019\"/>\n;{{flag|Iraq}}\n* [[Iraqi Army]]<ref name=\"World Air Forces 2019\"/>\n;{{Flag|Kazakhstan}}\n* [[Military of Kazakhstan]]<ref name=\"World Air Forces 2019\"/>\n;{{Flag|Kyrgyzstan}}\n* [[Military of Kyrgyzstan]]<ref name=\"World Air Forces 2019\"/>\n;{{LBY}}\n* [[Libyan Air Force]]<ref name=\"World Air Forces 2019\"/>\n[[File:Russian Air Force Mil Mi-24P Dvurekov-3.jpg|thumb|A Russian Air Force Mil Mi-35P]]\n;{{Flag|Mali}}\n*[[Military of Mali Air Force|Air Force of Mali]]<ref name=\"World Air Forces 2019\"/>\n;{{Flag|Mozambique}}\n* [[Military of Mozambique]]<ref name=\"World Air Forces 2019\"/>\n;{{MYA}}\n* [[Myanmar Air Force]]<ref name=\"World Air Forces 2019\"/>\n;{{Flag|Namibia}}\n* [[Namibian Air Force]]<ref name=\"World Air Forces 2019\"/>\n:{{Flag|Nicaragua}}\n*[[Nicaraguan Air Force]]<ref name=\"World Air Forces 2019\"/>\n;{{Flag|Niger}}\n* [[Air Force of Niger]]<ref name=\"World Air Forces 2019\"/>\n;{{Flag|Nigeria}}\n* [[Nigerian Air Force]]<ref name=\"World Air Forces 2019\"/>\n;{{PRK}}\n* [[North Korean Air Force]]<ref name=\"World Air Forces 2019\"/>\n;{{Flag|North Macedonia}}\n* [[Air Force of North Macedonia]]<ref name=\"World Air Forces 2019\"/>\n;{{PAK}}\n* [[Pakistan Army]]<ref name=\"World Air Forces 2019\"/>\n;{{PER}}\n* [[Peruvian Air Force]]<ref name=\"World Air Forces 2019\"/>\n[[File:Mi-24 Airshow 2007 Hungary 01.JPG|thumb|Hungarian Mi-24]]\n;