lan\u2019s Big Boo|publisher=Route Publishing|year=2016|isbn=978-1901927689}}\n*{{Cite book|first=Clinton|last=Heylin|title=Trouble In Mind: Bob Dylan's Gospel Years: What Really Happened|publisher=Route Publishing|year=2017|isbn=978-1901927726}}\n*{{Cite book|first=Clinton|last=Heylin|title=No One Else Could Play That Tune: The Making and Unmaking of Bob Dylan's 1974 Masterpiece |publisher=Route Publishing|year=2018|isbn=978-1901927764}}\n*{{Cite book|first=John|last=Hinchey|title=Like a Complete Unknown: The Poetry of Bob Dylan\u2019s Songs, 1962-1969|publisher=Stealing Home Press|year=2002|isbn=0-9723592-0-6}}\n* {{cite book|first=John|last=Hughes|title=Invisible Now: Bob Dylan in the 1960s|publisher=Routledge|year=2016|isbn=978-1138268760}}\n* {{cite book|first=Patrick|last=Humphries|title=Oh No! Not Another Bob Dylan Book|publisher=Square One Books|year=1991|isbn= 1-872747-04-3}}\n* {{cite book|first=Roy|last=Kelly|title=Bob Dylan Dream: My Life With Bob|publisher=Pembury House Publishing|year=2015|isbn=978-0992995683}}\n* {{cite book|first=David|last=Kinney|title=The Dylanologists: Adventures in the Land of Bob|year=2014|publisher=Simon & Schuster|isbn=978-1-4516-2692-6}}\n* {{cite book|first=Daniel|last=Kramer|title=Bob Dylan: A Portrait of the Artist's Early Years|year=1991|publisher=[[Plexus Publishing]]|isbn=0-85965-188-6}}\n* {{cite book|first=Daniel|last=Kramer|title=Bob Dylan: A Year and A Day|year=2016|publisher=[[Taschen]]|isbn=978-3836547604}}\n* {{cite book|first=C.P.|last=Lee|title=Like The Night: Bob Dylan and the Road to the Manchester Free Trade Hall|publisher=[[Helter Skelter (books)|Helter Skelter]] |year=1998|isbn=1-900924-07-2}}\n*{{Cite book|first=C. P.|last=Lee|title=Like a Bullet of Light: The Films of Bob Dylan|publisher=Helter Skelter|year=2000|isbn=1-900924-06-4|url=https://archive.org/details/likebulletofligh00cple}}\n* {{cite book|first=Greil|last=Marcus|authorlink=Greil Marcus|title=[[Invisible Republic|Invisible Republic: Bob Dylan